wiki.summary: "Good Good" is a song by American singers Usher, Summer Walker and Atlanta-based rapper 21 Savage. It was released on August 4, 2023 as the lead single from Usher's upcoming ninth studio album Coming Home (2024). The song was produced by Mel & Mus. Read more on Last.fm.
